            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E4%B8%8E%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E4%B8%8E%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胃癌的发病与哪些因素相关#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%98%8E%E6%98%BE%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%98%8E%E6%98%BE%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胃癌早期没有明显症状#</span></a>医生表示，①家族史，即遗传性因素。②幽门螺杆菌感染。关注幽门螺杆菌感染的状态，并进行根除。③环境因素。包括高盐摄入、维生素缺乏等。④心理压力、焦虑、生活不规律等。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>   <a href="http://t.cn/A6O7Hmmp" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a> ]]></description>
